(0) INTRODUCTION
  1. By downloading, installing or using RealTrainModUnofficial (the "Mod"),
     you agree to these terms.
  2. The Mod is NOT released under an open source license (MIT / GPL / LGPL
     etc.). Anything not expressly permitted here is prohibited.

(1) PRIVATE USE
  1. You may use the Mod freely as long as you do not pass it to third
     parties. This includes downloading, installing, playing, backing up,
     and modifying it for your own private use.

(2) MODIFICATION AND PORTING  -- CONTACT REQUIRED --
  1. Creating, publishing or distributing modified or ported versions is
     prohibited in principle.
  2. You MUST contact Sunnygo and obtain permission in advance if you wish to:
     a. Port the Mod to a Minecraft version other than 1.21.1 (incl. patches)
     b. Create a patch, add-on or modified build that changes the Mod's behaviour
  3. Contact
     - GitHub Issue : https://github.com/325-Sunnygo/RealTrainModUnofficial/issues
     - The RTMU Discord server

(3) REDISTRIBUTION
  1. Redistributing the Mod or the files inside it is prohibited in principle,
     whether modified or unmodified.
  2. The following are permitted as exceptions:
     a. Installing the Mod on a multiplayer server you operate, and
        distributing it to the players who join that server.
     b. Publishing videos, streams and screenshots made using the Mod.
  3. Inclusion in a ModPack requires prior permission from Sunnygo. Sunnygo may
     request removal or takedown of the Mod from any ModPack.
  4. Do not direct people to any download source other than the official URL above.

(4) COMMERCIAL USE
  1. Selling the Mod or the files inside it is prohibited, whether modified or not.
  2. Monetising videos and images created with the Mod is permitted.

(5) DISCLAIMER
  1. Sunnygo is not liable for any damage arising from use of the Mod.

(6) THIRD-PARTY WORKS
  The Mod contains works by the following authors, included with their
  permission. Rights to those parts remain with their respective authors.

   - RealTrainMod / NGTLib  --  ngt5479

   - KaizPatchX  --  (c) Kaiz_JP and other authors 2021

   - SignalControllerMod  --  masa

(7) PREVIOUS VERSIONS
  1. Versions up to and including v1.0.3 were released under LGPL-3.0.
     LGPL-3.0 grants cannot be revoked retroactively, so anyone who already
     received those versions retains their LGPL-3.0 rights to them.
  2. These terms apply to versions published after these terms were adopted.

(8) CHANGES
  1. Sunnygo may change these terms without notice.
  2. These terms apply indefinitely.
